          "desc": "FutureForge Hackathon 2026 is a virtual innovation challenge designed to bring together developers, designers, builders, and technology enthusiasts from across the globe. Participants will collaborate, create, and showcase impactful solutions that address real-world problems using emerging technologies.\n\nWhether you're passionate about AI, Web Development, Blockchain, Cybersecurity, Cloud Computing, or Open Innovation, this hackathon provides a platform to transform ideas into working products, learn from fellow innovators, and gain valuable hands-on experience.\n\nJoin us for an exciting journey of creativity, problem-solving, and innovation as we forge the future, one build at a time.\n\nWhat to Expect\n\n\ud83d\ude80 Build innovative projects\n\ud83e\udd1d Collaborate with talented peers\n\ud83d\udca1 Solve real-world challenges\n\ud83c\udfc6 Compete for exciting prizes\n\ud83c\udf10 Network with the tech community\n\ud83d\udcda Learn and grow through practical experience",
