          "desc": "\ud83d\ude80 Welcome to HyperFusion 2K26, an 8-hour offline hackathon organized by the Department of Computer Science & Engineering, JIS College of Engineering, Kalyani, West Bengal.\n\nHyperFusion is a platform where passionate developers, designers, and innovators come together to collaborate, solve real-world challenges, and build impactful technology solutions. Whether you're a first-time hacker or an experienced participant, HyperFusion is your opportunity to learn, create, and showcase your skills.\n\n\ud83d\udcc5 Event Details\n\ud83d\udccd Location: JIS College of Engineering, Kalyani, West Bengal, India\n\u23f0 Duration: 8 Hours\n\ud83d\udcdd Registration Deadline: 18 July 2026\n\ud83d\udcbb Hackathon Date: 24 July 2026\n\ud83d\udc65 Team Size: 2\u20134 Members\n\ud83c\udf93 Eligibility: Open to all college students\n\nThe event serves as a platform for bright minds from diverse backgrounds to come together and develop impactful solutions to real-world challenges. Through intensive ideation, mentorship, teamwork, and innovation, participants will transform creative concepts into functional prototypes capable of driving meaningful change.\n\nAt HyperFusion, we believe that innovation thrives at the intersection of knowledge, creativity, and determination. The hackathon encourages participants to explore emerging technologies, enhance their technical skills, and engage with a vibrant community of innovators and industry professionals.\n\nWhether you are an experienced hacker or a first-time participant, HyperFusion offers a unique opportunity to learn, build, network, and compete in an environment that celebrates technological advancement and entrepreneurial thinking.\n\nJoin us as we fuse ideas, technology, and talent to shape the future.",
